TextEng: The henchman has been selected by the PC Master.
Henchman leaves group and stands where he is.
Text: 부하가 그룹을 떠나 현재 위치에 섭니다.

TextEng: Henchman leaves group and returns to central location.
Text: 부하가 그룹을 떠나 중앙 위치로 돌아갑니다.

TextEng: Henchman asks what tactics the PC wishes to change.
Text: 부하가 PC가 어떤 전술을 변경하고 싶은지 묻습니다.

TextEng: Henchman asks how far the PC wants him to stand away.
Text: 부하가 PC가 얼마나 떨어져 서기를 원하는지 묻습니다.

TextEng: Henchman agrees to look through PC's backpack and report anything unusual.
Text: 부하가 PC의 배낭을 살펴보고 이상한 점을 보고하기로 동의합니다.

TextEng: Henchman asks what spell to cast.
Henchman asks what target to cast the spell on.
Text: 부하가 주문을 어떤 대상에게 시전할지 묻습니다.

TextEng: The henchman asks what you wish to talk about.
Henchman asks if the PC wants something else.
Text: 부하가 PC가 다른 것을 원하는지 묻습니다.

TextEng: The henchman asks what else the player wishes to discuss.
Text: 부하가 플레이어가 무엇을 더 논의하고 싶은지 묻습니다.

TextEng: The henchman has less than 100% HP.
The henchman has less than 50% HP.
The henchman has less than 25% HP.
Henchman returns to normal level-up scheme.
Henchman is using the standard level-up scheme.
The henchman was fired, after initial conversation.
The henchman was fired, it is Chapter 3, first time talked to.
The henchman was fired, it is Chapter 2, first time talked to.
The henchman was fired, it is Chapter 1, first time talked to.
The henchman stays where he is.
The henchman joins with the PC.
The henchman wishes to speak to the PC Master.
Henchman will hold off until later.
Random conversation #1 (does NOT relate to a specific event or place... can take place any time or place after joining)
Text: 랜덤 대화 #1 (특정 이벤트나 장소와 관련 없음... 합류 후 언제 어디서나 발생 가능)

TextEng: Context conversation #1 (relates to a specific event/place or has a specific pre-condition before it can be said)
Text: 상황별 대화 #1 (특정 이벤트/장소와 관련되거나 발생 전 특정 전제 조건 필요)

TextEng: The henchman had died, is being spoken to in the Realm of the Reaper.
Text: 부하가 죽었습니다, 사신의 영역에서 대화 중입니다.

TextEng: The henchman stays where he is.
The henchman had died, is being spoken to after being raised.
Text: 부하가 죽었다가 부활한 후 대화 중입니다.

TextEng: The henchman is spoken to by someone other than his master.
Text: 부하가 주인이 아닌 다른 사람과 대화 중입니다.
